44:04.000Z","msg":"80蚊交租"},{"pid":"c034b781854b7e7e64d0cdfab604ed7a0a41983f","tid":444341,"uid":121464,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:46:58.000Z","msg":"四片簿牛肉收人$120 牛丸 窄肉 河粉又係拎貨既 成本（唔計租）$12都比多佢 想呃香港人 too simple always naive"},{"pid":"191ac8492a9834e2da838e0d43e78c0a238ea102","tid":444341,"uid":35870,"like":47,"dislike":13,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完個新聞<br />\n佢地學得一個月<br />\n係咪真係有質素保証<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n幾多廚師訓練超過數年<br />\n先煮得出應有既味道<br />\n設計靚就靚啦<br />\n食物質素真係唔敢講</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未食過邊可以咁快判斷<br />\n而家係食實力，唔係食年資<br />\n得中國人先成日論資排輩，開口埋口老字號，傳統做法，做整出黎係垃圾<br />\n我認為呢種諗法唔要得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2613199431ea854aabf6801e47d3cad2bb4baecb","tid":444341,"uid":35870,"like":14,"dislike":8,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四片簿牛肉收人$120 牛丸 窄肉 河粉又係拎貨既 成本（唔計租）$12都比多佢 想呃香港人 too simple always naive</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要係好味<br />\n唔係成本<br />\n一碗拉麵成本都可以好低<br />\n<br />\n香港雲吞麵之所以上唔到大枱就係因為d人覺得係cheap野"},{"pid":"c35f879b664a3fa5b7ce2dfc4de644751d7bb888","tid":444341,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"曹博士牛河"},{"pid":"47b141d79a328de20b2129dc767df9900d833243","tid":444341,"uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:56:24.000Z","msg":"其實賣百幾蚊碗粉無乜問題<br />\n跑馬地係咁上下價錢<br />\n不過無乜噱頭、份量太少"},{"pid":"7f0ca7ed7753c3bd5b844772fd543d5c9dad5fa2","tid":444341,"uid":20809,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:56:26.000Z","msg":"老闆為求大家食得開心，120蚊打個和"},{"pid":"a40eeff5a868cc207d4bc2c647b414654713c0df","tid":444341,"uid":35870,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:56:33.000Z","msg":"要令到一樣野上到大枱，變成經典，貴係無可厚非，因為有錢先可以吸引人去做，有錢先可以獎勵到個廚師，有錢起碼可以搞下d裝修令成個氣氛更加好"},{"pid":"4c2a6def0291915ca92d7b2b73c126612296bbf1","tid":444341,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:04:53.000Z","msg":"中環玩具反斗城下面間懶高級餐廳以為係中環就可以亂黎<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔係on9 而家搞到賠租敗走"},{"pid":"a63b433701f404166945f49c8a8a96ed09b888b1","tid":444341,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>四片簿牛肉收人$120 牛丸 窄肉 河粉又係拎貨既 成本（唔計租）$12都比多佢 想呃香港人 too simple always naive</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要係好味<br />\n唔係成本<br />\n一碗拉麵成本都可以好低<br />\n<br />\n香港雲吞麵之所以上唔到大枱就係因為d人覺得係cheap野</blockquote><br />\n又唔可以咁比<br />\n拉麵個市場其實好單一<br />\n而且品牌方面做得好好<br />\n<br />\n河粉向來都係走廉價路線<br />\n而且面對同行平價泰國河啲挑戰事少<br />\n重要啲係香港河粉界一哥一直由我哋潮洲河粉企穏"},{"pid":"050e908a0e8522be2c3ce07752fae0995546ad11","tid":444341,"uid":28397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"同墨爾本 勇記 有無得 fihht 先"},{"pid":"b4ec3347b63e506092e8058f2777b7e3cb211393","tid":444341,"uid":28397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"用咩牛肉先 以前係佐敦食過一間 唔係嗰啲爛鬼邊爐牛 係用本地手切牛 牛脂肪同肉香濃好多"},{"pid":"4d1a0d980694de74edf52b6ce9f5a5c0310af974","tid":444341,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"米線都七十幾八十蚊碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2770319a440bb0e5208cc33a64f5cf35ae7ebf","tid":444341,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:16:52.000Z","msg":"學一個月賣120?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5aca2b39c950d4a521f61d325c765c1afdf071","tid":444341,"uid":54183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a15c44ead7525379559371674506ec568fc5